2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper mentions the use of wide area networks in grid computing, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.Distributed Systems - The paper discusses workload and resource management in grid infrastructures, which is a key area of research in distributed systems. 
4. cs.PF (Performance) - Load balancing is a technique used to improve the performance of distributed systems, which falls under the scope of performance evaluation and optimization. 
5. cs.SE (Software Engineering) - The paper discusses various load balancing mechanisms and algorithms, which can be considered as software engineering techniques for improving the performance of distributed systems.
